Class AbstractNut

java.lang.Object
  com.github.wuic.nut.AbstractNut
All Implemented Interfaces:
Nut, Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
ByteArrayNut, CompositeNut, FilePathNut, HttpNut, NotReachableNut, WebappNut
public abstract class AbstractNut
extends Object
implements Nut

Base implementation of the Nut interface. A Nut is often represented by a name and a NutType. This class already manages it.

Since:
0.3.0
